sequenceDiagram
    participant OC as OAuth Client
    participant MW as Client Auth Middleware
    participant TE as Thunder /oauth2/token

    OC->>MW: POST /oauth2/token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>Authorization: Basic base64(client_id:secret)
    MW->>MW: Extract & validate client credentials
    MW->>TE: Forward authenticated request
    TE->>TE: Validate grant_type allowed for client
    TE->>TE: Build access_token (JWT/RS256) with client_id as sub
    TE->>OC: Token Response {access_token, token_type, expires_in}
